data.description: SELLER VERY MOTIVATED!....Beautiful Home in an Established Residential Neighborhood. OPEN FLOOR PLAN. Minutes away from Fwy. Granite Countertops.  Tile flooring throughout living area, both baths, and hallways. Double pane window & sliding door. Family room has a wood burning fireplace. Master bedroom is good size & has large closet. Ceiling fans in living room & bedrooms. Large back yard with possible access from front to bring your toys. Sprinklers in front & backyard. New A/C Unit. Solar Panels buyers to assume solar lease.
